{"tid":2284551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲要白交稅？","createTime":"2020-11-13T11:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T08:01:06.000Z","uid":266601,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"14c9ee2d6ffaf73fd7433c6f86ac7654ecd8b5d0","tid":2284551,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:21:31.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">既然而家民主派都總辭啦<br />\n仲要我哋呢班香港公民交稅去養班狗官同賤聯<br />\n武肺下波都就爆<br />\n你估又會派翻10000蚊俾你咩？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n-$1交稅大法都出左爐十世 大家可以參考<br />\n<br />\n2020年 一蚊交稅方法整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1811809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1811809</a><br />\n<br />\n-將稅單被消失 點做仲洗教嘅<br />\n<br />\n一來我哋可以用呢個方法應該盡量令政府財政儲備赤字化佢，雖然不一定係長遠<br />\n<br />\n二來可以將自己付出左嘅血汗換翻黎嘅金錢放喺自己陣營嘅黃圈<br />\n<br />\n抗爭/運動/革命 的確係會冒風險同長久<br />\n但係大家都唔做 咪等住香港變香港巿囉<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命<br />\n民族自強，香港獨立<br />\n沒有暴徒，只有暴政</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a3a93930c8efae45e12029f5b9e44511d6929408","tid":2284551,"uid":160373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:23:05.000Z","msg":"逐蚊交緊<br />\n政府倒蝕"},{"pid":"fad474f301763cc1ccffa8b556520ba5446e877f","tid":2284551,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:25:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13b5074815f7cd80f197d844260b99281e74382b","tid":2284551,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:25:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2171410b99160439752689fd44960375e6cb691","tid":2284551,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03aa65013a4b1bd4be3821af88f9135eb600ef1a","tid":2284551,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:32:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a5d006a8a3b501d9ace06eee2671e04d57d0e56","tid":2284551,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"